{"tid":1901710,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"router 牌子問題一問","createTime":"2020-02-28T03:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T15:35:23.000Z","uid":350761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e635673be5877b1082275746a53d9e8b5438ab","tid":1901710,"uid":350761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"見好多巴絲話TP Link 唔好，因為早一年前買左TP link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網又冇指明有咩壞處，係咪因為支那做所以咁？ <br />\n想過轉ASUS，但性價比邊個好？ 定只針對支那問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者有冇其他牌子可推薦，因為對router 認識唔多<br />\n<br />\n（家至少三部腦上網，會同時打機。 所以有時一係ping 數高或有delay, 1000M 入屋plan, 搵人直接check 過 modem 係行到)"},{"pid":"b74107f83296161ed5623fc6f7666729fb87a4f4","tid":1901710,"uid":246419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:34:23.000Z","msg":"牙石86U"},{"pid":"e41ec6a83d00e3ba9e860de548236f370ebb69f8","tid":1901710,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:39:45.000Z","msg":"1年都ok<br />\n2年就壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我隻牙石就用咗5 6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ee2af52dec3ecdd695564c49a9dfeccf2b4eb9","tid":1901710,"uid":350761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e41ec6a83d00e3ba9e860de548236f370ebb69f8","tid":1901710,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:39:45.000Z","msg":"1年都ok<br />\n2年就壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我隻牙石就用咗5 6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:44:25.000Z","msg":"我用tp link 試過用到6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.g