moji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:33:18.000Z","msg":"RBK 幾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我見好似要配埋佢既 router 先得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:36:06.000Z","msg":"RBK20好似 唔記得了 一套過買<br />\n一部router連一部子衛星機"},{"pid":"4b0eee3a464a9f3b4faeb39790829e62019b9412","tid":1901710,"uid":156926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"用開linksys覺得好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfbf24a2be8f95cd4b5f5d4a4affd180fed0212","tid":1901710,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"TPLINK最大問題一定係實扑差,依樣絕對係大陸牌子常見問題.<br />\n件貨個FW本身未TUNE好就賣出街.所以你一出就買就預左實唔少小問題.<br />\n到FW成熟就到某某機發現有乜問題但係無跟進或者遲遲唔跟進<br />\n佢地個FW本身都係唔多功能架啦.<br />\n<br />\n海外型號就多數用料比較好,內銷就第一水後用料差<br />\n<br />\n路由器本身硬體問題反而唔大<br />\n基本上都算係耐操既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過大陸廠既野通常都係衰係個FW或者火牛身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n計你買同等配備<br />\n台廠.外國廠1200蚊隻<br />\ntplink,tenda賣700既話<br />\n你可能會考慮下<br />\n但係以bcm4708/bcm4709依加既價錢差距<br />\n600 vs 800<br />\n你就未必會諗大陸牌子了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmt7261果d,若果部大陸機有信得過既openwrt刷既話<br />\n幾十蚊唔怕用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買到asus,nethear要400-500"},{"pid":"f58d73ae2e51af22dd0e1b5797e16accb4d7fc34","tid":1901710,"uid":350761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b0eee3a464a9f3b4faeb39790829e62019b9412","tid":1901710,"uid":156926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"用開linksys覺得好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\